# Upgrading firmware

* [General description](http://raspberryalphaomega.org.uk/2014/06/14/upgrading-bus-pirate-firmware/)

Steps

* Download the zip file with upgrade package: [Downloads](https://github.com/DangerousPrototypes/Downloads), [suggested download](https://github.com/DangerousPrototypes/Downloads/blob/master/BusPirate.package.v6.1.zip)
* Get the ```pirate-loader-lnx``` programm from downloaded zip file.
* Get the firmware hex file [here](https://github.com/mikebdp2/Bus_Pirate/tree/master/package_latest/BPv3)
* Check help of pirate-loader
* shorten GND and PGC headers on the buspirate board (these are holes, not pins)
* execute ```pirate-loader --hello``` and then upgrade or whatever 